message.body: I think D told kristin the dinner times, but I'll be drinking beer and watching golf earlier than that if you want to come. I'm sure Donna would trick kristin into helping her with something while we sat downstairs and watched phil choke.
Do you guys want a bike rack for your car or truck that fits in the hitch? I can't use it anymore.
I will def try to get there a bit earlier. Will take a look at the bike rack today.
